INSERT INTO categories (id, name, description) VALUES (2, 'Programming', 'Dive into the world of coding with our comprehensive programming courses. Whether you''re a beginner or an experienced developer, our courses cover a variety of programming languages and topics, from Python and JavaScript to Java and C++. Learn to build websites, mobile apps, software, and more, and unlock endless possibilities in the digital realm.');
INSERT INTO categories (id, name, description) VALUES (5, 'Design', 'Unleash your creativity and unleash the power of design with our inspiring courses. From graphic design and user experience (UX) design to web design, animation, and multimedia production, our courses cover a variety of design disciplines. Learn to create stunning visuals, develop intuitive user interfaces, and bring your creative ideas to life. Whether you''re a novice designer or a seasoned professional, our courses will help you sharpen your skills and stay ahead in the ever-evolving world of design.');
INSERT INTO categories (id, name, description) VALUES (4, 'Business', 'Elevate your business acumen with our wide range of business courses. From entrepreneurship and management to finance, strategy, and leadership, our courses cover all aspects of running a successful business. Gain practical skills, learn from real-world case studies, and discover innovative approaches to solving business challenges. Whether you''re an aspiring entrepreneur or a seasoned executive, our courses will help you achieve your business goals.');
INSERT INTO categories (id, name, description) VALUES (3, 'Marketing', 'Explore the dynamic field of marketing through our expert-led courses. From digital marketing strategies to social media advertising and market research, our courses provide you with the knowledge and skills needed to excel in today''s competitive market. Gain insights into consumer behavior, learn to create compelling campaigns, and take your marketing career to new heights.');
INSERT INTO categories (id, name, description) VALUES (1, 'Data Science', 'Delve into the world of data science and analytics with our cutting-edge courses. Learn to extract valuable insights from data, master machine learning algorithms, and unleash the power of data-driven decision-making. Whether you''re interested in data visualization, predictive modeling, or big data technologies, our courses will equip you with the skils needed to thrive in this rapidly evolving field.');
